data.description: Welcome to your Desert Oasis... Pride of ownership is definitely shown in this move in ready 3 bedroom 2 bath home with a retreat style backyard. The home has many recent updates in the kitchen, living room, formal dining/family room, bathrooms, flooring,  Arizona room, pergola with 6 person hot tub, updated pool decking, and painted sidewalks. All major appliances included along with an additional refrigerator.  Interior window shutters on all front windows and new minispilt in the Arizona room. Don't miss this one of kind gem! Come see it today!
